        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "The specification is here https://spec.editorconfig.org/#glob-expressions. It does not state clearly how to handle this case.\n\nHowever, my reading of the specification text is that `**/` _should_ only match subdirectories, not sibling files.\n\nIf you want to match `Dockerfile` at any level, that is what the plain `Dockerfile` pattern does. No glob needed. ",
