        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Oh ok thank you for your insight.\n\nI knew that using plain `Dockerfile` matched at any level, but since some utilities (like editorconfig-checker) were behaving differently I wanted to have neovim's take on the matter.\n\nI'll let you close the issue if you believe that should not change.\n\nThanks again for your time.",
